question: List the names of the dances, their origins, and their popularity scores, ranking them from most to least popular, where the scores range from 70 to 85.
sql_query1: SELECT DanceName, Culture, Popularity FROM "DanceTable" WHERE Popularity BETWEEN 70 AND 85 ORDER BY Popularity DESC;
sql_query2: SELECT DanceName, Geographical_Area, Popularity FROM "DanceTable" WHERE Popularity BETWEEN 70 AND 85 ORDER BY Popularity DESC;
sql_query3: SELECT DanceName, Culture, Geographical_Area, Popularity FROM "DanceTable" WHERE Popularity BETWEEN 70 AND 85 ORDER BY Popularity DESC;
interpretation1: List the names of the dances, their origin culture, and their popularity scores, ranking them from most to least popular, where the scores range from 70 to 85
interpretation2: List the names of the dances, their origin geographical area, and their popularity scores, ranking them from most to least popular, where the scores range from 70 to 85
interpretation3: List the names of the dances, their origin culture and geographical area, and their popularity scores, ranking them from most to least popular, where the scores range from 70 to 85
sql_query_general: SELECT DanceName, Origin, Popularity FROM "DanceTable" WHERE Popularity BETWEEN 70 AND 85 ORDER BY Popularity DESC;

question: Display the origins of dances with popularity above 80 along with their popularity value.
sql_query1: SELECT Culture, Popularity AS MostPopular FROM "DanceTable" DanceTable WHERE Popularity > 80;
sql_query2: SELECT Geographical_Area, Popularity AS MostPopular FROM "DanceTable" DanceTable WHERE Popularity > 80;
sql_query3: SELECT Culture, Geographical_Area, Popularity AS MostPopular FROM "DanceTable" DanceTable WHERE Popularity > 80;
interpretation1: Display the culture of dances with popularity above 80, along with their popularity value.
interpretation2: Display the geographical area of dances with popularity above 80, along with their popularity value.
interpretation3: Display the culture and geographical area of dances with popularity above 80, along with their popularity value.
sql_query_general: SELECT Origin, Popularity AS MostPopular FROM "DanceTable" DanceTable WHERE Popularity > 80;
